---
title: Cranberry-Drizzled Duck with Watercress Salad and Mashed Potatoes
description: Cranberry sauce is for more than just turkey. Here, we’re using it to make crispy, pan-seared duck breasts truly dazzle. The rich poultry is enlivened by its tart fruitiness, resulting in a wave of bold flavors that travel over the tongue. Add some buttery mashed potatoes and a peppery watercress salad to the side, and you’ve got a meal that is sure to be a favorite in your kitchen all year round.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5a99ca8330006c758c6dc3f2-c1daf006.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cranberry-drizzled-duck-breasts-5a99ca8330006c758c6dc3f2-f76db439.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cranberry-drizzled-duck-breasts-5a99ca8330006c758c6dc3f2
time required: 45 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 960 kcal
  fat: 70 g
  saturated fat: 25 g
  carbohydrates: 60 g
  sugar: 20 g
  protein: 32 g
  fiber: 9 g
  sodium: 640 mg
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
